{"type": "article", "id": 21220, "title": "置物架", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-25T07:30:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 38, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021151425OeDcKiEqoC4WwRY.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这一系列的置物架来自墨尔本的品牌 Bride &amp; Wolfe，它有圆形、三角形或方形等多个模型，上面分布了粗细不同的圆孔，将原有的几何外观又重新分割了一次。圆孔可以钉上照片或者加一个小的挂钩，上面还带有一到两块隔板，适合放一些装饰类的小东西。这个置物架将不同的物品紧凑地放在一个区域，像是开了一个小窗，能改变单调的环境。有多个形状和颜色可选，售价 195 美元起，<a href=\"http://www.brideandwolfe.com.au/collections/the-mesh-series\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150835DirjaVvbRo7mzOh5.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1189\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.10092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150836z5UqkQN0CDPWZiJf.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"725\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.20833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150836RjnkN7y6CUiXbABK.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"738\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.23\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150837Cq1i6OfH7lkFB8Pt.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"705\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.175\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016072615083864iL2VTKEywaFlPe.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"646\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.07666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}